+# Exploration 002 Report - Anti-Circuit Dossier On The Frozen Step-4 Sheet
+
+## Goal
+
+Apply the frozen Step-4 family ledger and pass/fail sheet to the anti-circuit
+families:
+
+- `F_BM`:
+  Beltrami-cancellation / mirror-complete family
+- `F_DT(delta, eta)`:
