/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/runtime/results/codex-patlas-standalone-20260331T130634Z-receptionist-94037.md:9:- `Lamb-vector / Helmholtz-projected form` is claiming exact Beltrami/gradient isolation: expose the first-order-looking nonlinear piece and separate the projection debt. The local record says Tao-style averaging preserves the generic CZ/LP/Sobolev structure, while localization reintroduces the projection/pressure/commutator burden, so the specialness is washed out at the estimate level. See [Step-005 Exploration 003](/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/steps/step-005/explorations/exploration-003/REPORT.md#L77) and [Projected And Vorticity Rewrites Must Pay Localization Debt](/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/library/factual/exact-rewrite-obstruction-audit/projected-and-vorticity-rewrites-must-pay-localization-debt.md#L13).
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/runtime/results/codex-patlas-standalone-20260331T130634Z-receptionist-94037.md:29:- The exact-rewrite Tao screen is distinct from the De Giorgi sharpness record because De Giorgi is already overdetermined by `beta = 4/3` and the H^1/BMO, atomic, and interpolation failures. See [Vasseur pressure step 1](/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/vasseur-pressure/steps/step-001/RESULTS.md#L13) and [Vasseur pressure step 2](/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/vasseur-pressure/steps/step-002/RESULTS.md#L11).
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/runtime/results/codex-patlas-beyond-de-giorgi-run-001-judge-02.md:6:The judgment marks the attacker as mostly correct, with the main valid points being: the original chain screened too late at the estimate level, leaned too hard on algebraic rewrites, and applied the Tao filter too late. I treated the Beltrami and SQG-template critiques as partially valid rather than fully valid, because those ideas still have use as fragility screens and motivating analogies if handled narrowly.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/runtime/results/codex-patlas-beyond-de-giorgi-run-001-judge-02.md:8:The refined chain now front-loads the Tao screen, defines the exact bottleneck estimate and what counts as a real gain before any rewrite work, kills the branch immediately if no estimate-level improvement appears by Step 2, and treats Beltrami behavior only as a handoff condition to the geometry branch. I set the probability of a presentable result at `0.66`, with most of that coming from a realistic negative/obstruction memo rather than a true positive breakthrough.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/runtime/results/codex-patlas-beyond-de-giorgi-step-005-explorer-001.md:5:`De Giorgi truncation` is rejected as already exhausted by the recorded pressure/`beta = 4/3` negatives, and `vorticity stretching localization` is rejected as mismatched to the rewrite shortlist and already killed on the fixed geometry package.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/runtime/results/codex-patlas-beyond-de-giorgi-step-002-explorer-002.md:6:Bottom line: the Tao screen narrows the route hard. `local Beltrami deficit or alignment` collapses as a primary route, `vorticity-direction coherence` and `tube coherence or persistence` remain only weakly informative alone, and the only live survivor is the hybrid `direction coherence plus tube persistence`. The recommendation is to proceed to Step 2 only in that narrowed form.
